Bunny Droid : The Human Slayer
Bunny droid is one of the special droids, She has an almost perfect body structure like humans in general. But Her hatred towards mankind is undeniable, She is ice cold and has a matchless shooting ability, She is known as " THE HUMAN SLAYER " despite having a waifu material face.
